{"tid":2334504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人並不是與政府交戰　而是與自己交戰　與香港人自己的心障交戰","createTime":"2020-12-21T08:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T09:46:17.000Z","uid":261647,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"113463c55e72746277ee5a6e0591b44137299dd7","tid":2334504,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T08:18:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158669130427357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10158669130427357&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=7e34074c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10158669130427357</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你希望的是維護這制度，你是選擇了荒謬，荒謬的不是政府而是你自己，政府與其人員倒很清楚自己在做甚麼：出賣靈魂以求在制度取利。他們很清楚服從制度，制度的不公平就對他們有利。<br />\n<br />\n市民才是荒謬的，他們被制度壓迫，抱怨制度不公平，可是因為懶得想像制度倒塌後他們要怎樣解決各種問題，所以他們不斷說制度是好的，只是政府人員沒有用好制度。<br />\n<br />\n但如果人不好，你沒辦法驅逐，而制度又取決訴主事者的善惡，這又怎可能是好的制度？你又為何維護他？只因為這制度也給你好處，讓你可以沒政治才能也可以當議員裝成參政，當律師贏得社會尊崇？捨不得這些小利，令你對制度的邪惡本質支吾其詞，那你何嘗不是這荒謬的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n所以香港人並不是與政府交戰，而是與自己交戰，政府是香港人的法律信仰下產生形體的邪神，他是香港人自己的心障。"},{"pid":"c571f24c95ea5890eb0e732c9fba6e89dcee029e","tid":2334504,"uid":232766,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T08:34:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"green\">鄭立幾時先肯分享佢喺<strong><span class=\"red\">中國</span></strong>營商同籌集資金嘅心得？<br />\n<br />\n另外，唔知台灣人會否視佢嘅公司為陸資？<br />\n<br />\n點解佢可以喺中國營商，出入中國，但同時日日將「抗爭」掛喺口邊？</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8ec5606549047b89f01cb604d880ea90148fa4c9","tid":2334504,"uid":249979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fXmS5pP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfXmS5pP.jpg&h=0ed63bf7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"545812e63cc5df3e1d9c8247dcffa5981e8508d2","tid":2334504,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:36:05.000Z","msg":"由抗爭到戰爭，由覺醒到破局需要嘅心態。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2219689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2219689</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5eb48688694e7ce75790fa6b3115136a8c79e5e3","tid":2334504,"uid":37817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ec5606549047b89f01cb604d880ea90148fa4c9","tid":2334504,"uid":249979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fXmS5pP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfXmS5pP.jpg&h=0ed63bf7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:40:33.000Z","msg":"入戲太深<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8459baa308c1833142ba4253a6f8bd6028ee353","tid":2334504,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5eb48688694e7ce75790fa6b3115136a8c79e5e3","tid":2334504,"uid":37817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8ec5606549047b89f01cb604d880ea90148fa4c9","tid":2334504,"uid":249979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:30:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fXmS5pP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfXmS5pP.jpg&h=0ed63bf7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:40:33.000Z","msg":"入戲太深<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"現實難做，唔代表要放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7dbf9161564b068af279359ecfedf677df8927","tid":2334504,"uid":78907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T09:46:17.000Z","msg":"個個都想唔改變就有自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}